{"_id":"7KlEepvS7kPVfhi8","name":"Protection arcanique [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous tendez votre main et tracez un symbole de protection dans les airs. Jusqu'&agrave; la fin de votre prochain tour, vous obtenez la r&eacute;sistance contre les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts contondants, tranchants et perforants inflig&eacute;s par des attaques avec arme.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/air-burst-sky-2.jpg","effects":[{"_id":"hSJwDFveFD3Zsbqd","flags":{"dae":{"stackable":false,"specialDuration":"None","transfer":true}},"changes":[{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"piercing","mode":0,"priority":5},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"bludgeoning","mode":0,"priority":5},{"key":"data.traits.dr.value","value":"slashing","mode":0,"priority":5}],"disabled":true,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":1,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/air-burst-sky-2.jpg","label":"Protection arcanique","origin":"Item.DK6Wxpme39pzjBta","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"7WdWejShqmCb74WZ","name":"Désorientation [Légilimancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Une cr&eacute;ature de votre choix que vous pouvez voir et &agrave; port&eacute;e du sort doit r&eacute;ussir un jet de sauvegarde de Sagesse. Si elle &eacute;choue, vous pouvez d&eacute;cider du d&eacute;placement de la cible lors de son tour. Vous ne pouvez la mettre directement en danger par ce d&eacute;placement, en provoquant des attaques d'oppotunit&eacute; ou en la faisant se diriger vers un gouffre ou une zone enflamm&eacute;e par exemple.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":18,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":false,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/evil-eye-eerie-1.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8t31wy4cgOtedmQl","name":"Projectile élémentaire [Hémomancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous cr&eacute;ez un projectile d'&eacute;nergie magique &eacute;l&eacute;mentaire et le lancez vers une cr&eacute;ature dans la port&eacute;e du sort. Faites une attaque &agrave; distance avec un sort contre la cible.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le projectile est constitu&eacute; d'une substance sombre et bouillonante. Une cr&eacute;ature touch&eacute;e par ce missile subit 2d8 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de poison et doit r&eacute;ussir un jet de sauvegarde de Constitution ou &ecirc;tre empoisonn&eacute;e jusqu'&agrave; la fin de son prochain tour.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs.</strong> Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts augmentent de 1d8 pour chaque niveau au-del&agrave; du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":27,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"pact","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d8"}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Fire Bolt"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/beam-red-2.jpg","effects":[{"_id":"bRg4Qc2UjwxpduHJ","flags":{"dae":{"stackable":false,"specialDuration":"None","transfer":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":1,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/beam-red-2.jpg","label":"Projectile élémentaire","origin":"Item.76U6m4G0yIRsi53e","tint":"","transfer":false}]}
{"_id":"BQFvysPQwS42zd82","name":"Piège temporel [Temps]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quand vous lancez ce sort, vous cr&eacute;ez un cercle magique de 1,50 m&egrave;tre de rayon au sol. Le pi&egrave;ge est presque invisible et demande un jet d'Intelligence (Investigation) r&eacute;ussi contre le DD de sauvegarde de votre sort pour &ecirc;tre d&eacute;cel&eacute;.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le pi&egrave;ge se d&eacute;clenche lorsqu'une cr&eacute;ature de taille P, M ou G marche sur le sol dans le rayon du sort. Cette cr&eacute;ature doit r&eacute;ussir un jet de sauvegarde de Charisme ou bien &ecirc;tre magiquement fig&eacute;e dans le temps. La cr&eacute;ature est entrav&eacute;e jusqu'&agrave; ce que le sort se termine.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Une cr&eacute;ature entrav&eacute;e peut effectuer un jet de sauvegarde de Charisme &agrave; la fin de chacun de ses tours, mettant fin &agrave; l'effet sur elle-m&ecirc;me en cas de r&eacute;ussite. La cr&eacute;ature ou quelqu'un d'autre qui peut l'atteindre peut aussi utiliser son action pour effectuer un jet d'Intelligence (Arcanes) contre le DD de sauvegarde de votre sort. En cas de r&eacute;ussite, l'effet d'entrave prend fin.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Apr&egrave;s le d&eacute;clenchement du pi&egrave;ge, le sort se termine lorsque le pi&egrave;ge ne retient plus aucune cr&eacute;ature.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":8,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/wind-grasp-eerie-2.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"E9IWi8GR65PFxG4l","name":"Détection de la magie [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pour la dur&eacute;e du sort, vous percevez la pr&eacute;sence de magie &agrave; 9 m&egrave;tres ou moins de vous. Si vous percevez de la magie de cette mani&egrave;re, vous pouvez utiliser votre action pour discerner une faible aura enveloppant une cr&eacute;ature ou un objet visible dans la zone qui pr&eacute;sente de la magie. Vous d&eacute;terminez aussi l'&eacute;cole de magie, le cas &eacute;ch&eacute;ant. <br />Le sort peut outrepasser la plupart des obstacles mais il est bloqu&eacute; par 30 cm de pierre, 2,50 cm de m&eacute;tal ordinaire, une mince feuille de plomb ou 90 cm de bois ou de terre. </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":9,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":true,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Detect Magic"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/light-blue-2.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"EafNauTEwMAA6v3P","name":"Charme-personne [Psychomancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous pouvez tenter de charmer un humano&iuml;de que vous pouvez voir &agrave; port&eacute;e. Ce dernier doit effectuer un jet de sauvegarde de Sagesse, avec un avantage &agrave; son jet si vous ou vos compagnons le combattez. En cas d'&eacute;chec, il est charm&eacute; jusqu'&agrave; la fin de la dur&eacute;e du sort ou jusqu'&agrave; ce que vous ou vos compagnons cherchiez &agrave; lui nuire. La cr&eacute;ature charm&eacute;e vous consid&egrave;re comme un bon ami. Quand le sort prend fin, la cr&eacute;ature sait que vous l'avez charm&eacute;e.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs.</strong> Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, vous pouvez cibler une cr&eacute;ature suppl&eacute;mentaire pour chaque niveau au-del&agrave; du niveau 1. Les cr&eacute;atures doivent se trouver &agrave; 9 m&egrave;tres maximum les unes des autres lorsque vous les ciblez.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":9,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translat