{"_id":"NdGJsmBSaOn8d7Dz","name":"Coup au but [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous tendez votre main et pointez un doigt en direction d'une cible &agrave; port&eacute;e. Votre magie vous aide &agrave; trouver une petite faille dans les d&eacute;fenses de votre cible. Lors de votre prochain tour, vous obtenez l'avantage sur votre premier jet d'attaque contre la cible, &agrave; condition que le sort ne soit pas d&eacute;j&agrave; termin&eacute;. </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":9,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":0,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":false,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"True Strike"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/enchant-sky-1.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"Nj9fIjZnyY3y7a2W","name":"Sangsue [Hémomancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Un rayon d'&eacute;nergie rouge cr&eacute;pitante est projet&eacute; sur une cr&eacute;ature &agrave; port&eacute;e, formant un arc sanguin continu entre la cible et vous. Effectuez une attaque &agrave; distance avec un sort contre la cr&eacute;ature. Si vous touchez, la cible subit 1d12 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de poison et vous r&eacute;cup&eacute;rez 1d4 points de vie. &Agrave; chacun de vos tours, pour la dur&eacute;e du sort, vous pouvez utiliser votre action pour infliger automatiquement 1d12 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de poison &agrave; la cible et r&eacute;cup&eacute;rez 1d4 points de vie. Le sort se termine si vous utilisez votre action pour faire autre chose qu'infliger ces d&eacute;g&acirc;ts, si la cible se retrouve hors de la port&eacute;e du sort, ou si elle obtient un abri total contre vous.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs.</strong> Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts initiaux sont augment&eacute;s de 1d12 pour chaque niveau au-del&agrave; du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":9,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d12","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"1d4","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"pact","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/rip-magenta-2.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"OnXjQcns3hh1y1gU","name":"Identification [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous choisissez un objet que vous devez toucher durant toute la dur&eacute;e du sort. Si l'objet est magique ou impr&eacute;gn&eacute; de magie, vous apprenez ses propri&eacute;t&eacute;s et comment les utiliser, s'il requiert un lien pour &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute; et le nombre de charges qu'il contient, le cas &eacute;ch&eacute;ant. Vous apprenez si des sorts affectent l'objet et quels sont ces sorts. Si l'objet a &eacute;t&eacute; cr&eacute;&eacute; par un ou plusieurs sorts, vous apprenez quels sorts ont permis de le cr&eacute;er.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Si vous touchez une cr&eacute;ature durant toute la dur&eacute;e du sort, au lieu d'un objet, vous apprenez quels sorts l'affectent actuellement, le cas &eacute;ch&eacute;ant.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"minute","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"object"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":true,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"une perle d'une valeur d'au moins 100 po et une plume de hibou","consumed":false,"cost":100,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Identify"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/light-eerie-1.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"P5XTVxi1LEIX45Hj","name":"Armure [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous touchez une cr&eacute;ature consentante qui ne porte pas d'armure, et une force magique de protection l'englobe jusqu'&agrave; ce que le sort prenne fin. La CA de la cible passe &agrave; 13 + son modificateur de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute;. Le sort prend fin si la cible enfile une armure ou si vous prenez une action pour interrompre le sort.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"_sheetTab":"details","dynamiceffects":{"effects":[{"modSpecKey":"data.attributes.ac.value","value":"13 + @abilities.dex.mod","mode":"=","targetSpecific":false,"id":1,"itemId":"KWepVspVtjeboJgf","active":true,"_targets":[]}],"alwaysActive":false,"equipActive":true},"dae":{"activeEquipped":false,"alwaysActive":false}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/protect-blue-1.jpg","effects":[{"_id":"XRkvYT9cV0BX5oJc","flags":{"dae":{"transfer":false,"stackable":false,"specialDuration":"None"}},"changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.ac.value","value":"13 + @abilities.dex.mod","mode":5,"priority":5}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":