{"_id":"hKpjb3lTmZJk6ajh","name":"Main arcanique [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Une main compos&eacute;e d'&eacute;nergie r&eacute;siduelle appara&icirc;t &agrave; un point pr&eacute;cis choisi &agrave; port&eacute;e. La main expire &agrave; la fin de la dur&eacute;e du sort ou si elle est r&eacute;voqu&eacute;e au prix d'une action. La main dispara&icirc;t si elle se retrouve &agrave; plus de 9 m&egrave;tres du lanceur de sorts ou si ce sort est jet&eacute; une nouvelle fois.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le lanceur de sorts peut utiliser son action pour contr&ocirc;ler la main. La main peut manipuler un objet, ouvrir une porte ou un contenant non verrouill&eacute;, ranger ou r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer un objet d'un contenant ouvert, ou bien verser le contenu d'une fiole. La main peut &ecirc;tre d&eacute;plac&eacute;e jusqu'&agrave; 9 m&egrave;tres &agrave; chaque fois que vous l'utilisez.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">La main ne peut attaquer, activer des objets magiques ou transporter plus de 5 kg.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"space"},"range":{"value":9,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":0,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Mage Hand"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/ice_16.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"hhM2FwhZVkr45M4I","name":"Projectile magique [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous cr&eacute;ez trois fl&eacute;chettes de force magique d'un bleu lumineux. Chaque fl&eacute;chette atteint une cr&eacute;ature de votre choix que vous pouvez voir et dans la limite de port&eacute;e du sort. Chaque projectile inflige 1d4 + 1 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force &agrave; sa cible. Les fl&eacute;chettes frappent simultan&eacute;ment, et peuvent frapper une ou plusieurs cr&eacute;atures.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs.</strong> Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, il cr&eacute;e une fl&eacute;chette additionnelle pour chaque niveau au-del&agrave; du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":36,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"Une fléchette par niveau d'emplacement de sort","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + 1","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Magic Missile"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/fire-arrows-magenta-1.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"htWlZYMvj0bpXryZ","name":"Rayon caustique [hémomancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Un jet d'&eacute;nergie rougeoyante &eacute;mane de vous dans une ligne de 9 m&egrave;tres de long et de 1,50 m&egrave;tres large dans une direction que vous choisissez. Chaque cr&eacute;ature dans la ligne doit r&eacute;ussir un jet de sauvegarde de Dext&eacute;rit&eacute; ou voir leur peau bouillir pour la dur&eacute;e du sort ou jusqu'&agrave; ce qu'une cr&eacute;ature utilise son action pour r&eacute;duire les effets sur elle-m&ecirc;me ou sur une autre cr&eacute;ature. Une cr&eacute;ature qui ne fait rien contre les effets du sort subit 2d4 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts d'acide au d&eacute;but de chacun de ses tours.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs.</strong> Quand vous lancez ce sort avec un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts augmentent de 2d4 pour chaque niveau au d&eacute;l&agrave; du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":9,"width":1.5,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["2d4","poison"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"pact","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Ray of Frost"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/beam-acid-1.jpg","effects":[{"_id":"42RAszM1UPi5iBIk","flags":{"dae":{"stackable":false,"specialDuration":"None","transfer":false}},"changes":[],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":10,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/beam-acid-1.jpg","label":"Rayon caustique","origin":"Item.0IVrWj6iyS7VTfhm","tint":"","transfer":false}]}
{"_id":"kHylUY7MumboOElZ","name":"Détection du poison et des maladies [Hémomancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pour la dur&eacute;e du sort, vous pouvez percevoir la pr&eacute;sence et localiser les poisons, les cr&eacute;atures venimeuses, et les maladies dans un rayon de 9 m&egrave;tres autour de vous. Vous identifiez &eacute;galement le type de poison, de cr&eacute;ature venimeuse, ou de maladie. Le sort peut outrepasser la plupart des obstacles mais il est bloqu&eacute; par 30 cm de pierre, 2,50 cm de m&eacute;tal ordinaire, une mince feuille de plomb ou 90 cm de bois ou de terre.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":10,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":9,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"level":1,"school":"div","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"pact","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{"babele":{"translated":true,"hasTranslation":true,"originalName":"Detect Poison and Disease"}},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/air-burst-jade-2.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"lG5bxfoB7QqoizMz","name":"Epée des arcanes [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous faites apparaitre une arme d'&eacute;nergie pure adoptant la forme d'une &eacute;p&eacute;e &agrave; une main. Vous pouvez utiliser l'arme en faisant des jets d'attaque de sort au corps &agrave; corps contre vos ennemis. L'arme inflige 1d8 + votre modificateur de caract&eacute;ristique d'incantation d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force. Tant que le sort est actif et que vous maintenez votre concentation, vous pouvez faire apparaitre et disparaitre l'arme sans utiliser d'action.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs</strong>. Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts inflig&eacute;s par l'arme augmente de 1d8 tous les deux niveaux au-del&agrave; du niveau 3 pour un total de 2d8 au niveau 3 et de 3d8 au niveau 5.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/enchant-sky-3.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"nrsJ8PivFt7uV3QL","name":"Diversion [Légilimancie]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Un humano&iuml;de de votre choix, que vous pouvez voir et &agrave; port&eacute;e, doit r&eacute;ussir un jet de sauvegarde de Sagesse. S'il &eacute;choue, il ne vous consid&egrave;re pas comme dangereux et ne peut d&eacute;cider de vous attaquer que si aucune autre cible hostile ne se trouve dans son champ de vision, et ce pendant la dur&eacute;e du sort. Toute action aggressive de votre part envers la cible ou un alli&eacute; de la cible que la cible peut voir met fin au sort.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":18,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"always","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/explosion-royal-1.jpg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"pJImOk22htbrQlCe","name":"Absorption des éléments [Elémentalisme]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le sort capte une partie de l'&eacute;nergie entrante, ce qui r&eacute;duit son effet sur vous et la stocke pour votre prochaine attaque au corps &agrave; corps. Vous obtenez une r&eacute;sistance &agrave; ce type de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts jusqu'au d&eacute;but de votre prochain tour. De plus, la premi&egrave;re fois que vous touchez avec une attaque au corps &agrave; corps lors de votre prochain tour, la cible subit 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts suppl&eacute;mentaires du type d'&eacute;l&eacute;ment cibl&eacute;, et le sort se termine.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs. </strong>Quand vous lancez ce sort en utilisant un emplacement de sort de niveau 2 ou sup&eacute;rieur, les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts suppl&eacute;mentaires augmentent de 1d6 pour chaque niveau d'emplacement au-del&agrave; du niveau 1.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"ue vous prenez lorsque vous subissez des dégâts d'acide, de froid, de feu, de foudre ou de tonnerre"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":1,"school":"abj","components":{"value":"","vocal":false,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"pact","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/runes-orange-1.jpg","effects":[{"_id":"ydgaVk1WLsciwOTP","flags":{"dae":{"stackable":false,"specialDuration":"None","transfer":true}},"changes":[],"disabled":true,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":1,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null},"icon":"systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/runes-orange-1.jpg","label":"Absorption des éléments","origin":"Item.yzJ62jkIePItfT07","tint":"","transfer":true}]}
{"_id":"qLi9Z2pYeBbhuSOW","name":"Enchainement arcanique [Arcanes]","permission":{"default":0,"NOPkQVbnCZiWZF74":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vous brandissez l'arme utilis&eacute;e pour l'incantation du sort et effectuez une attaque au corps &agrave; corps avec cette arme contre une cr&eacute;ature &agrave; 1,50 m&egrave;tre ou moins de vous. Si vous touchez, la cible subit les effets normaux de l'attaque et une &eacute;nergie arcanique jaillit de cette cible pour aller frapper une autre cr&eacute;ature de votre choix que vous pouvez voir et qui se trouve dans un rayon de 1,50 m&egrave;tre autour de la premi&egrave;re cr&eacute;ature. Cette seconde cr&eacute;ature subit des d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force &eacute;gal au modificateur de votre caract&eacute;ristique d'incantation.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de ce sort augmentent suivant votre niveau. Au niveau 5, l'attaque de corps &agrave; corps inflige 1d6 d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force suppl&eacute;mentaires &agrave; la premi&egrave;re cible, et les d&eacute;g&acirc;ts de force subis par la seconde cible atteignent 1d6 + le modificateur de votre caract&eacute;ristique d'incantation. Les deux jets de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts augmentent chacun de 1d6 suppl&eacute;mentaire aux niveaux 10 (2d6 et 2d6) et 15 (3d6 et 3d6).</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enéride","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"Attaque de corps à corps avec une arme"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1.5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"util","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["(floor(@attributes.hd /5))d6","force"]],"versatile":"@mod+(floor(@attributes.hd /5))d6"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scal